OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FA British satellite earth station is
OL,7,Fset to play a role in Nasa launching
OL,8,Fits Artemis II mission to the Moon.
OL,10,FA spacecraft is due to set off from
OL,11,Fthe US on Wednesday to take astronauts
OL,12,Faround the Moon for the first time in
OL,13,Fmore than 50 years.
OL,15,FFour astronauts ` three American and
OL,16,Fone Canadian ` will take the seats in
OL,17,Fthe vessel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FThe Artemis II launch from the Kennedy
OL,7,FSpace Centre in Florida must take
OL,8,Fplace between Wednesday and next
OL,9,FMonday or it will have to wait until
OL,10,Fthe end of the month for another
OL,11,Fchance.
OL,13,FGoonhilly Earth Station, near Helston,
OL,14,FCornwall, will help to track the Orion
OL,15,Fspacecraft as it travels around the
OL,16,FMoon and back to Earth.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FThe satellite and space company has
OL,7,Fbeen involved in events such as
OL,8,Fbroadcasting the Apollo 11 Moon
OL,9,Flanding to the world in 1969, and
OL,10,Flanding a commercial spacecraft on the
OL,11,FMoon for the first time.
OL,13,FIn 2022, the site previously provided
OL,14,Fcritical communication and tracking
OL,15,Fsupport for Nasa's Artemis I.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FMatthew Cosby, chief technology
OL,7,Fofficer of the Goonhilly Earth
OL,8,FStation, said: "Artemis II marks a
OL,9,Fsignificant milestone in humanity's
OL,10,Freturn to the Moon, and we're proud
OL,11,Fthat the capabilities developed here
OL,12,Fin Cornwall are contributing to that
OL,13,Fmission.
OL,15,F"From our site, we will support
OL,16,Ftracking of the Orion spacecraft,
OL,17,Fshowcasing our readiness for future
OL,18,Fcrewed Artemis missions.
OL,26,@pD@POUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,F"At the same time, we are positioning
OL,7,Fthe UK to play a key role in Nasa's
OL,8,Flonger-term Moon to Mars exploration
OL,9,Fstrategy."
OL,11,FGoonhilly is also working with the UK
OL,12,FSpace Agency and Nasa to explore
OL,13,Fsolutions for near-real time space
OL,14,Fweather measurements.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
