OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FBaroness Lloyd, the UK government
OL,7,Fminister responsible for space, added:
OL,8,F"From broadcasting the Apollo 11 Moon
OL,9,Flanding to the world in 1969, to now
OL,10,Fsupporting Nasa's return to the Moon
OL,11,Fwith Artemis II, Goonhilly's rich
OL,12,Fheritage in space communication
OL,13,Fcontinues to inspire.
OL,15,F"It's fantastic to see Cornwall once
OL,16,Fagain at the heart of a truly historic
OL,17,Fmoment in human spaceflight.
OL,26,@pD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,F"This partnership with Nasa shows what
OL,7,FBritish expertise and innovation can
OL,8,Fachieve on the world stage, while
OL,9,Fcreating opportunities for skilled
OL,10,Fjobs and growth right here in the UK."
OL,12,FAt a press conference on Monday night
OL,13,FUK time, leaders at Nasa hailed
OL,14,Finternational collaboration as they
OL,15,Fconfirmed the vehicle, system and crew
OL,16,Fwere ready.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
