OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,FAssociate administrator of Nasa, Amit
OL,7,FKshatriya, told reporters: "This crew
OL,8,Fis an international crew for a reason.
OL,9,FOne of the most amazing things about
OL,10,Fthe space station, I think the most
OL,11,Famazing thing, was the partnership
OL,12,Fthat was developed to operate that
OL,13,Fmachine.
OL,15,F"As I said in my opening, we're going
OL,16,Fto need the free nations of the world
OL,17,Fto collaborate to build even more
OL,18,Fambitious architectures as we expand
OL,19,Four range of action throughout the
OL,20,Fsolar system.
OL,26,@oD@\OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1774929839
OL,3,CCornish radiocommunication station to
OL,4,Csupport Nasa Moon mission
OL,6,F"There's no question in my mind
OL,7,Fpartnership is fundamental to that."
OL,9,FCharlie Blackwell-Thompson, launch
OL,10,Fdirector, called it "an exciting time
OL,11,Ffor this team and our crew and really
OL,12,Four nation and the world".
OL,14,FChief flight director Emily Nelson
OL,15,Fsaid: "The opportunity is immense for
OL,16,Fus to finally get the opportunity to
OL,17,Fsend our crew farther than anyone's
OL,18,Fgone before, and it's an incredible
OL,19,Fmoment for the Artemis generation and
OL,20,Fwe're excited and we are ready to
OL,21,Fpress."
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@dO]rD@UOUtD@YO]wD@GOU}D@GO]
